DESCRIPTION:Volunteers are invited to help Sycamore maintain habitat at ou
 r preserves and gain hands-on experience in land stewardship! Weed Wrangle
  events are fun and educational opportunities to learn how to identify and
  control the invasive plants that are negatively impacting natural areas a
 nd other green spaces. The focus for this work day will be the identificat
 ion and control of garlic mustard. ***This event was rescheduled to May 10
  and moved to 11am.***
