UID:fa7ffc2ce14cb0d6c378423256021e87@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Sycamore Land Trust has expanded our annual “Arbor Day Tree 
 Giveaway” to distribute more than 1\,000 native tree saplings for free i
 n southern Indiana! On Saturday\, April 29\, 2023\, visit Bloomingfoods Ea
 st &amp\; Near West to pick up a free native tree seedling\, get planting 
 advice\, renew your membership\, and celebrate everything that makes trees
  amazing!  The Arbor Day Tree Giveaway in Bloomington starts at 10am and 
 will end at 1pm or when supplies run out. For more information\, visit syc
 amorelandtrust.org/free-trees.
