BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Conservation Conversation: Carroll Ritter\, author of Magnificent 
 Trees of Indiana
DTSTART:20260623T190000
DTEND:20260623T210000
UID:d983e3d4422ced6cc03923d2085cdab4@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:On June 23\, 2022 at 7pm\, Carroll D. Ritter will join our Con
 servation Conversation virtual lecture series to discuss his new book Magn
 ificent Trees of Indiana and how it can be an inspiration to appreciate ou
 r grand forest heritage. Featuring the fascinating history of Indiana&#821
 7\;s trees\, remaining old-growth forest pieces and the state champions\, 
 along with trees of stunning beauty and unique forms stimulated the creati
 on of this book. The objective was to create not another field guide\, but
  an enjoyable\, educational read\, complimented by beautiful photography.
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2022/06/conservation-conversation-carrol
 l-ritter-author-of-the-magnificent-trees-of-indiana/
X-SOURCE:Sycamore Land Trust
END:VEVENT
